{
  "stem": "12029.2",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But one day, in that block of flats where we live was a lot of people, some of which were richer and some of which were very poor, which were starving from hunger.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Then my father called all the people from the block of flats to our flat.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And he spoke to them, and he said, look here.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "We've got to help our poor brothers and sisters.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And he decided-- they decided to make a kitchen to feed everybody-- all those poor people, that they should get food every day, because otherwise they will die from starvation.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And not only that say didn't have food, but it was typhus also in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "People were dying from typhus.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And then the formed another-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] they form in the ghetto, like, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] for sick people-- I don't know how to say it.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not a hospital-- you see, they form that if somebody's ill and got typhus, they put him in.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--to Isolation.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And in case in a block of flats somebody had typhus, they used to close up the block of flats, go in to the flats like to disinfect them.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But they actually didn't disinfect.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They wanted money, or they used to see what somebody got there that they could blackmail.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And a lot of blackmail was going on in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "If somebody was rich, then they used to blackmail him in a different.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And my father was blackmailed very, very often.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, I remember.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "For instance, when they came, and they found something, let's say, for instance, chocolate-- you couldn't manufacture chocolate-- then if they found that was manufactured chocolate, then say said, come on.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Give us money.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And this very often was happening.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
